window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>From Gwyneth Paltrow’s modern lifestyle brand goop comes the Audible Original <i>The goop Pursuit</i>, a four-part audio series taking listeners on an intimate journey of learning and unlearning.</p> <p>“Finding Beauty”</p> <p>Author, LGBTQIA+ activist, and beauty maven Jodie Patterson explores capital-“B” Beauty through intimate interviews with her personal \"collage of women\"— dynamic friends, mentors, and public figures from whom she draws inspiration and confidence. Patterson shares her own relationship to beauty— how she redefined her understanding and belief in beauty, and what drew her back to the transformative power it holds for all of us today.</p> <p><b>This episode contains mature themes and listener discretion is advised.</b></p>"; 
